backs me a hundred percent.

05:11.280 --> 05:13.555
- Look, we'II talk about it at dinner tonight.
- Around and around

05:13.680 --> 05:16.114
- Yeah, me whole family. Penelope!
- And around-

05:16.240 --> 05:19.312
Do that somewhere else, will ya?
Ask your mum to make a cup of tea!

05:19.440 --> 05:21.749
Mom, make Dad a cup of tea.

05:26.280 --> 05:29.272
Mom! Make Dad a cup of tea!

05:29.400 --> 05:31.675
- Me too.
- What?

05:32.880 --> 05:35.952
Tea? Oh, yes.

05:40.560 --> 05:43.028
- He got it! Look at that!
- Oh, man.

05:43.160 --> 05:45.435
Did you see that?
That was unreal.

06:13.640 --> 06:16.677
Muriel's back.

06:16.800 --> 06:18.870
Muriel, did you steal this dress?

06:19.000 --> 06:21.912
- No.
- Where'd you get the money to buy it?

06:22.040 --> 06:25.032
You haven't had a job in two years.

06:25.160 --> 06:28.232
- Mum gave it to me.
- Is this true?

06:28.360 --> 06:31.591
Um, no, I don't think so.

06:31.720 --> 06:34.359
Find the receipt. Go on!

06:37.760 --> 06:39.637
