getting arrested at weddings!

10:39.600 --> 10:41.477
You're useless.

10:43.480 --> 10:45.357
You're all useless.

10:49.760 --> 10:52.149
A bunch of useless no-hopers.

10:55.120 --> 10:57.873
Bill! Bill!

10:58.000 --> 10:59.877
- It's Deidre Chambers.
- What a go!

11:00.000 --> 11:01.558
- What a coincidence!
- What a coincidence!

11:01.680 --> 11:03.910
Deidre, pull up a chair.
Penelope, shift out.

11:04.040 --> 11:06.429
- Deidre, Victor Keinosuke and his mate Akira.
- Hello. Hello.

11:06.560 --> 11:08.596
All the way from China-
Uh, Japan.

11:08.720 --> 11:11.280
Deidre's a sales representative
for Radiant Cosmetics.

11:11.400 --> 11:15.439
- Beauty consultant, Bill.
- Sorry. Beauty consultant.

11:15.560 --> 11:17.790
" Sales representative"
sounds so common.

11:17.920 --> 11:21.754
I advise women on the right
lipstick, base and eyeliner.

11:21.880 --> 11:25.350
Of course, you'd know all about make-up.
Your wives are probably geishas.

11:26.720 --> 11:28.472
You look lovely, Deidre.

11:28.600 --> 11:31.353
Muriel, how was that wedding?

11:31.480 --> 11:34.631
- She was arrested.
- That's lovely.

11:34.760 --> 11:37.957
Don't you wish you were
22 again, Betty?

11:38.080 --> 11:40.435
Remember that age?

11:40.560 --> 11:42.516
Oh, yes. What?

11:42.640 --> 11:45.200
I bet you were a terror
when you were 22.

11:45.320 --> 11:47.754
Bill, was she a terror?

11:47.880 --> 11:49.836
Where's Charlie Chan
with that food?

11:49.960 --> 11:53.430
Oh, yes, where is he?

11:53.560 --> 11:56.518
Anyone? Oh, wait.
I think we've got a winner over here.

11:56.640 --> 11:58.517
Two new bars through there.

11:58.640 --> 12:01.154
Here she comes.
Give her a bit of a hand.

12:09.600 --> 12:12.751
Your dad was telling me
you're unemployed, Muriel.

12:15.480 --> 12:17.835
Would you like to work for me?

12:34.360 --> 12:36.874
- What's wrong?
- What's the matter?

12:37.000 --> 12:38.956
Yeah, tell us.
We won't tell anyone.

12:47.560 --> 12:50.552
Hello.

12:50.680 --> 12:54.036
Don't bottle it up, Tania.
You've got to let it out.

12:54.160 --> 12:56.958
You can tell us what happened.
We won't tell anyone.

13:02.600 --> 13:06.639
He- He couldn't do it...

13:08.360 --> 13:11.432
so I- you know.

13:13.080 --> 13:15.913
And I noticed there
was lipstick on it.

13:16.040 --> 13:18.759
- On what?
- His dick!

13:20.440 --> 13:23.113
He said he was having an affair.

13:23.240 --> 13:26.755
Who with?

13:26.880 --> 13:30.509
- Rose Biggs.
- Rose Biggs?

13:30.640 --> 13:33.757
Well, he said they don't sleep together.
She only sucks him off.

13:33.880 --> 13:36.713
Why?

13:36.840 --> 13:40.196
- Out of respect for me.
- Bitch.

13:40.320 --> 13:44.472
- Bastard.
- What am I gonna do? I'm a bride!

13:44.600 --> 13:47.637
I'm supposed to be euphoric!

13:47.760 --> 13:50.035
Come on the holiday with us!

13:50.160 --> 13:53.470
Cash in your ticket to Bali
and have your honeymoon with us.

13:53.600 --> 13:56.637
- Yeah.
- Yeah, come on, Tan.

13:56.760 --> 13:59.149
All right.

13:59.280 --> 14:02.033
We are gonna have the best time.
I'm so excited!

14:02.160 --> 14:04.720
What holiday?

14:06.240 --> 14:08.754
Just Hibiscus Island.

14:08.880 --> 14:11.599
We didn't think that you could afford it
because you don't have a job.

14:11.720 --> 14:16.635
Yes, I do. I got one last night.
I'm a beauty consultant.

14:16.760 --> 14:19.593
Let's tell her. We were
gonna tell her after the holiday...

14:19.720 --> 14:21.756
but I think we should tell her now.

14:25.000 --> 14:26.877
- Muriel-
- Wait!

14:28.360 --> 14:31.238
Let her finish her Orgasm.

14:51.320 --> 14:54.710
