14:54.840 --> 14:57.559
But that's just us.
We're ragers.

14:57.680 --> 15:01.116
People invite us to parties, and
they know we'II just have a good time.

15:01.240 --> 15:03.390
- We're mad.
- Party, party, party.

15:03.520 --> 15:06.398
That's our image.
You know what I mean.

15:07.720 --> 15:10.109
We're mad.

15:10.240 --> 15:12.754
We don't want you
hanging around us any more.

15:18.560 --> 15:20.630
I didn't steal the dress.
It was a mistake.

15:20.760 --> 15:22.751
It's not the dress, it's you.

15:22.880 --> 15:25.952
We've told you a thousand times how
to do your hair, but you never listen.

15:26.080 --> 15:28.674
- You never wear the right clothes.
- You're fat.

15:28.800 --> 15:32.236
You listen to '70s music.
This is the '90s.

15:32.360 --> 15:35.432
- We all listen to the Baby Animals.
- And Nirvana.

15:35.560 --> 15:39.314
- You bring us down, Muriel.
- You embarrass us.

15:39.440 --> 15:42.989
I, I know I'm not normal,
but I'm trying to change.

15:43.120 --> 15:45.554
I'm trying to become more like you,
more of a-

