friends on your own level.

16:03.160 --> 16:06.994
Like I found Chook.
He's up on my level.

16:07.120 --> 16:12.274
Marrying him was
the happiest day of my life.

16:15.800 --> 16:17.950
I love him so much!

16:21.880 --> 16:24.519
That bastard!
I'II show him.

16:24.640 --> 16:28.349
I'II go on this holiday
and I'II sleep with a thousand men!

16:28.480 --> 16:30.357
I'm not nothing.

16:30.480 --> 16:33.756
Muriel, can't you think of anyone
but yourself? Tania's upset.

16:33.880 --> 16:35.950
I'm not nothing!

16:36.080 --> 16:38.753
Well, nobody said that.

16:38.880 --> 16:42.475
Oh, please don't chuck me
out of the group!

16:45.960 --> 16:50.158
Muriel. Muriel, you're
embarrassing us again!

16:57.880 --> 17:00.678
And Perry kicks!
He picks it up!

17:00.800 --> 17:03.598
" Go yourself! Go yourself!"
