go driving at night...

18:34.560 --> 18:38.155
but he's only showing her
his developments.

18:38.280 --> 18:41.511
- His what?
- His building sites.

18:50.480 --> 18:53.119
I'm gonna be a success, Mum.

18:53.240 --> 18:56.152
I'm gonna get married,
and I'm gonna be a success.

18:56.280 --> 19:00.876
I know you are. Your dad just
wants to be proud of you, that's all.

19:01.000 --> 19:05.278
I'II show him.
I'II show them all.

19:07.400 --> 19:09.994
And now, everybody a big round of
applause as we welcome to the stage...

19:10.120 --> 19:12.076
act three in Hibiscus Island
Talent Quest.

19:12.200 --> 19:15.954
The Tropical Delights!
Let's hear it for the girls! Thank you!

19:24.120 --> 19:28.910
The tide is high
but I'm holding on

19:29.040 --> 19:33.591
I'm gonna be your number one

19:33.720 --> 19:40.273
I'm not the kind of girl
who gives up just like that

19:40.400 --> 19:42.277
Oh, no, oh

19:45.800 --> 19:48.075
- Hey, whose shout is it?
- Cheryl's.

19:48.200 --> 19:51.954
Cheryl's shout!

19:52.080 --> 19:54.355
- Muriel!
- Where did she get the money?

20:06.240 --> 20:09.232
Hi. What a coincidence.

20:11.120 --> 20:15.113
You're a mental case!
You keep away from us!

20:21.120 --> 20:24.157
You're got no dignity, Muriel.

20:49.760 --> 20:51.955
- Are you Muriel Heslop?
- No.

20:54.480 --> 20:56.038
- Yes, you are.
- Why?

20:56.160 --> 20:58.037
I don't know why.
You just are.

20:58.160 --> 21:00.196
Rhonda Epinstall.
We were in high school together.

21:00.320 --> 21:03.153
You dropped out in year ten.
I dropped out in year eleven.

21:03.280 --> 21:05.157
Ha! I knew it was you!

21:05.280 --> 21:08.033
- Hey, swap seats?
- Yeah, indeed.

21:08.160 --> 21:11.596
So, are you married now?

21:11.720 --> 21:13.756
- What?
- Well, you said you weren't Muriel Heslop.

21:13.880 --> 21:16.314
If you changed your name,
I thought you must have got married.

21:16.440 --> 21:19.113
No. Yes.

21:19.240 --> 21:21.549
- I'm engaged.
- Anyone I know?

21:21.680 --> 21:24.592
- What? Who? Tim.
- Who? - What?

21:24.720 --> 21:27.359
- Tim who?
- Simms.

21:27.480 --> 21:31.314
Tim Simms.
Don't know him. What's he like?

21:31.440 --> 21:35.991
- Um, like no one.
- Smoke?

21:36.120 --> 21:39.157
- What?
- I shouldn't. I'm an asthmatic.

21:40.280 --> 21:42.032
- So where is he?
- Who?

21:42.160 --> 21:44.151
Tim Simms.

21:47.720 --> 21:49.836
I'm on to you.

21:49.960 --> 21:51.871
You're not wearing
an engagement ring.

21:52.000 --> 21:53.956
You're here
without your fiance.

21:54.080 --> 21:57.675
You're out for a good time,
aren't you, Muriel? A last fling?

21:57.800 --> 21:59.836
I suppose so.

21:59.960 --> 22:03.669
You are wicked! Well, stick
with me, 'cause I'm wicked too.

22:03.800 --> 22:07.588
My whole life is one last fling
after another.

22:07.720 --> 22:10.712
Hey, remember Tania Degano?
She got married, to Chook.

